 # Testing and Quality Assurance

## Performance Testing
- Implement performance profiling and monitoring tools
- Identify and resolve performance bottlenecks
- Create automated performance tests
- Monitor frame rates and memory usage

## Cross-Platform Testing
- Use cross-device testing for consistent performance
- Test on various browsers and devices
- Verify mobile-specific features
- Test different screen sizes and orientations

## Error Handling
- Implement error logging and crash reporting
- Set up proper debugging tools
- Handle browser-specific issues
- Implement appropriate workarounds

## Testing Strategy
- Write comprehensive unit tests for game logic
- Implement integration tests for game scenes
- Create automated performance tests
- Use mocks for external services
- Implement playtesting tools
- Set up analytics for gameplay balance

## CI/CD Integration
- Set up automated builds and testing
- Implement continuous integration
- Configure deployment pipelines
- Use global error and alert handlers
- Integrate crash reporting services